<br />

<br />
With a geerlok or trophy you'll only need to go as far as 285 to have a JC skill of 300, I wonder whether it will cap at 302 though... There had better be a new tradeskill title at 300 though.
<br />

<br />
Plat topaz until 255
<br />
Plat peri until 258
<br />
Plat star ruby to until 271
<br />
Plat ruby until 279
<br />
Plat diamond until 287
<br />
Velium amethyst until 300
<br />

<br />
Remember the key is to keep the combines green with geerlok and as close to your current skill as possible. The list above should do that fairly cost effectively.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
