No, its a general EQ upgrade. The usual rules apply in that you can get one general tradeskill over 200, but need to spend AA's to get more tradeskills past 200. But, once a tradeskill is at 201, its not capped until 300 (barring missing recipes such as Research which has only recipes to somewhere in the 220's).</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
